author: PlayStation
description:
Pre-order Tour De France 2025 Now: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10012764/


Get ready for the next generation of Tour De France! The upgrade to Unreal Engine 5 brings the most realistic experience yet, ride past iconic locations like the Champs-Elysées, Trouée d'Arenberg, Mont Ventoux, and more on your quest for the iconic Yellow Jersey. That’s not all either, with new multiplayer modes, private lobbies, a new refuelling system, and more.  

Slip on your Lycra cause France 2025 is coming to PlayStation 5 on June 5th. Pre-order now to get the collector jerseys! 

#ps5 #ps5games #tourdefrance #tourdefrance2025
title: Tour de France 2025 - Pre-order Trailer | PS5 Games
